  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted, W-CON-01 injected)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; 12 carry structured requiredLevel and achievedLevel integers. One factor — Model Form — is documented through a richly-written qualitative assessment narrative judged sufficient by the review team; structured level integers were inadvertently omitted from the record. Despite this gap, the overall decision record reflects an Accepted outcome, creating a factor-decision inconsistency (W-CON-01).",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-hemolysis-accepted",
